1. *Duguješ* mi još dvadeset evra, (You still owe me twenty euros.)
2. Nisam znao da *duguješ* toliko dugo, (I didn't know you owe so long.)
3. Pažljivo pogledaj sve što *duguješ*, (Carefully check everything you owe.)
4. Ona već duguje tako dugo da zaboravih, (She has been owing for so long that I forgot.)
5. Moraš da *duguješ* još par meseci, (You have to owe for a few more months.)